## 📊 Priority Matrix

| Feature | Effort | Impact | Infra Ready? |
|---|---|---|---|
| Public Share Links | Medium | 🔥🔥🔥 | ✅ DB + Types exist |
| Create Folder | Low | 🔥🔥🔥 | ✅ VFS has `mkdir` |
| Rename Files | Low | 🔥🔥🔥 | ✅ VFS has `rename` |
| Move / Copy | Low-Med | 🔥🔥🔥 | ✅ VFS has both |
| Search | Medium | 🔥🔥🔥 | Partial |
| Toast Notifications | Low | 🔥🔥 | None needed |
| Audit Log Viewer | Medium | 🔥🔥 | ✅ DB + Core exist |
| Upload Progress | Medium | 🔥🔥 | ✅ Chunk types exist |
| Real Metrics | Medium | 🔥🔥 | Partial |
| Per-Folder ACL | High | 🔥🔥 | ✅ DB + Types exist |
| Trash / Recycle Bin | Medium | 🔥🔥 | None |
| Group Management | Medium | 🔥 | ✅ DB exists |
| Storage Quotas | Medium | 🔥 | None |
| 2FA/MFA | High | 🔥 | ✅ Fields exist |
| Theme Toggle | Low | 🔥 | ✅ CSS vars exist |
| Mobile Layout | Medium | 🔥 | Partial |
| Text Editor | Medium | 🔥 | None |
| Image Thumbnails | Medium | 🔥 | None |

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Recommended starting order:** Create Folder → Rename → Move/Copy → Toast Notifications → Share Links → Search → Audit Logs
>
> This order maximizes value while building on existing infrastructure. The first four are low-effort with massive usability improvements.

